skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: gymnastics facts
des: Have you ever wanted to know more about the Final Five? Who they are, what they accomplished, at what age they were when they won all those medals in Rio at the 2016 Olympic games? Well, this skill helps do exactly that by providing users with fun facts about all 5 members of the team, and even more people involved with their success. Ask away!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
